<small>A [[phylogeny]] of the extant ant [[subfamily|subfamilies]].<ref>{{cite journal |author=Ward, Philip S |title=Phylogeny, classification, and species-level taxonomy of ants
(Hymenoptera: Formicidae)|journal=[[Zootaxa]] |volume=1668 |year=2007|pages=pp. 549&ndash;563 }}</ref><br/>
<nowiki>*</nowiki>Cerapachyinae is [[paraphyletic]]</small>}}
