| [[Neotropic ecozone|Neotropics]] ||align="right"| 2162
|-
| [[Nearctic ecozone|Nearctic]] ||align="right"| 580
|-
| [[Europe]] ||align="right"| 180
|-
| [[Africa]] ||align="right"| 2500
|-
| [[Asia]] ||align="right"| 2080
|-
| [[Melanesia]] ||align="right"| 275
